1
00:00:44,362 --> 00:00:49,137
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

2
00:00:49,650 --> 00:00:52,237
=Episode 28=

3
00:01:09,925 --> 00:01:10,512
(Wang Dongxue)

4
00:01:10,512 --> 00:01:13,150
(Tang Sihai)

5
00:01:13,325 --> 00:01:15,087
(Entity name:
Xuehai International Investment Ltd)

6
00:01:15,200 --> 00:01:17,362
(Certificate of Incorporation)

7
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:18,359
Wait,

8
00:01:18,680 --> 00:01:20,200
isn't this just a company document?

9
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:21,560
It's the registration info

10
00:01:22,079 --> 00:01:23,959
for an offshore company
in the Cayman Islands.

11
00:01:24,300 --> 00:01:24,840
Check it out.

12
00:01:32,175 --> 00:01:32,937
(Messages)

13
00:01:37,187 --> 00:01:39,450
(Take the USB drive.)
All texts with He Lian are here.

14
00:01:39,780 --> 00:01:41,159
- Check them immediately.
- On it.

15
00:01:47,079 --> 00:01:48,200
We have the evidence.

16
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:49,120
Let's get out of here.

17
00:01:58,550 --> 00:02:00,375
(Ye Chen)

18
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:02,239
(Tang Sihai,)

19
00:02:02,599 --> 00:02:03,799
(hurry over.)

20
00:02:04,275 --> 00:02:05,437
(It's time to settle this.)

21
00:02:10,925 --> 00:02:12,912
(Ye Chen: Thanks, Ms. Song.)

22
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:20,759
So, you were

23
00:02:20,759 --> 00:02:22,719
helping Ye Chen
with a distraction all along.

24
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:24,800
Was I?

25
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:36,639
Mr. Ye.

26
00:02:41,919 --> 00:02:43,639
I hated this place as a kid.

27
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:45,120
No freedom.

28
00:02:45,639 --> 00:02:46,560
No friends.

29
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:49,120
Mr. Quan forced me to train every day.

30
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:51,319
I just wanted a simple life,

31
00:02:52,162 --> 00:02:53,875
like other kids.

32
00:02:55,039 --> 00:02:56,039
Carefree.

33
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:58,439
Go wherever I wanted.

34
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:01,960
Even that was impossible.

35
00:03:06,175 --> 00:03:07,935
If it weren't for Madam Li,

36
00:03:08,225 --> 00:03:10,070
I don't know if I'd have made it.

37
00:03:11,225 --> 00:03:13,439
This is all thanks to you.

38
00:03:16,199 --> 00:03:16,759
Spit it out.

39
00:03:18,039 --> 00:03:19,080
What did you do?

40
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:21,360
When the time comes,

41
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:23,960
I'll tell you.

42
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:28,159
So, you won't
wake up until it's too late, huh?

43
00:03:30,120 --> 00:03:30,919
What is this?

44
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:32,879
Where did you get it?

45
00:03:33,560 --> 00:03:34,400
Tang Sihai,

46
00:03:35,199 --> 00:03:36,719
believe me, I'll end you right now.

47
00:03:45,280 --> 00:03:46,319
Tang Sihai,

48
00:03:46,687 --> 00:03:48,605
I'm avenging my parents today!

49
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:02,479
I saw it myself.

50
00:04:02,479 --> 00:04:03,680
Tang Sihai is badly hurt

51
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:04,560
and still in surgery.

52
00:04:05,020 --> 00:04:06,960
Wang Dongxue has everyone
searching for Ye Chen.

53
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:08,280
Ms. Song,

54
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:09,639
your plan worked.

55
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:14,199
It wouldn't have gone

56
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:16,039
so smoothly without you.

57
00:04:16,810 --> 00:04:17,599
Here's 100 million.

58
00:04:18,120 --> 00:04:18,840
You earned it.

59
00:04:20,039 --> 00:04:21,120
It's an honor to serve you,

60
00:04:21,479 --> 00:04:22,439
Ms. Song.

61
00:04:23,100 --> 00:04:24,390
Go upstairs and lie low for now.

62
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:25,720
Ye Chen

63
00:04:25,879 --> 00:04:27,279
should be here soon.

64
00:04:38,639 --> 00:04:39,519
What happened?

65
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:40,879
You're hurt.

66
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:42,000
I'm fine.

67
00:04:43,439 --> 00:04:44,750
This is Tang Sihai's blood.

68
00:04:45,160 --> 00:04:46,040
I stabbed him.

69
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:47,240
Mr. Ye,

70
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:48,639
that was reckless.

71
00:04:48,959 --> 00:04:49,879
He didn't

72
00:04:51,160 --> 00:04:52,480
just hurt Madam Li.

73
00:04:52,879 --> 00:04:54,279
He kept coming after me.

74
00:04:54,839 --> 00:04:56,240
He even killed my parents.

75
00:04:58,439 --> 00:04:59,879
It's him or me.

76
00:05:00,200 --> 00:05:01,890
How did things
get so bad between you two?

77
00:05:04,037 --> 00:05:04,995
Because of this.

78
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:06,399
Because of this...

79
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:09,040
Never mind that.

80
00:05:09,639 --> 00:05:10,439
I need to run.

81
00:05:10,959 --> 00:05:11,762
Ms. Song,

82
00:05:12,319 --> 00:05:13,199
I know you can help.

83
00:05:13,879 --> 00:05:14,439
Please,

84
00:05:14,839 --> 00:05:15,879
figure something out.

85
00:05:16,520 --> 00:05:17,680
Sit down and have some water.

86
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:18,399
I'll arrange it now.

87
00:05:18,399 --> 00:05:19,000
Okay.

88
00:05:29,519 --> 00:05:30,600
Thanks.

89
00:05:35,839 --> 00:05:36,680
Prepare a boat.

90
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:38,100
I need to get a friend out.

91
00:05:38,110 --> 00:05:39,040
As fast as possible.

92
00:05:45,519 --> 00:05:46,240
Donggang Pier.

93
00:05:46,639 --> 00:05:47,680
Depart in one hour.

94
00:05:50,839 --> 00:05:51,879
Thank you, Ms. Song.

95
00:05:52,519 --> 00:05:52,920
Really,

96
00:05:53,399 --> 00:05:53,800
thank you.

97
00:05:55,759 --> 00:05:56,800
Mr. Ye, what's wrong?

98
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:00,720
I feel

99
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:02,000
a bit dizzy.

100
00:06:06,639 --> 00:06:07,279
Mr. Ye.

101
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:08,639
Mr. Ye.

102
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:24,920
Congratulations, Ms. Song.

103
00:06:26,959 --> 00:06:28,000
Mission accomplished.

104
00:06:28,790 --> 00:06:30,079
How do you want to handle him?

105
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:33,800
Send him away.

106
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:51,959
Thanks for giving me the USB drive.

107
00:06:52,090 --> 00:06:53,199
Saved me a lot of trouble.

108
00:06:54,399 --> 00:06:54,839
You...

109
00:06:55,079 --> 00:06:56,240
Curious, aren't you?

110
00:06:56,310 --> 00:06:58,710
I clearly fainted, so why am I
standing here perfectly fine?

111
00:06:59,439 --> 00:07:00,079
Ms. Song,

112
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:01,959
it seems your background check

113
00:07:01,959 --> 00:07:03,199
on me wasn't thorough.

114
00:07:03,959 --> 00:07:05,519
Mr. Quan anticipated this.

115
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:07,439
Since I was a kid,
he tested me with all sorts

116
00:07:07,439 --> 00:07:08,800
of medicine to build resistance.

117
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:10,600
I'm not immune to everything,

118
00:07:10,959 --> 00:07:11,560
but your

119
00:07:11,759 --> 00:07:12,879
little tricks

120
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,160
won't fool me.

121
00:07:20,210 --> 00:07:21,639
You've been acting this whole time.

122
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:23,000
Learned from the best.

123
00:07:23,462 --> 00:07:25,319
Not only did I flush out Ms. Jiang,

124
00:07:25,319 --> 00:07:26,787
I also got you to hand over the drives

125
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:27,862
and exposed

126
00:07:28,319 --> 00:07:29,800
your true face.

127
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:32,560
Three birds, one stone. Why not?

128
00:07:33,639 --> 00:07:34,439
Tang Sihai,

129
00:07:35,199 --> 00:07:36,959
believe me, I'll end you right now.

130
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:43,600
Mr. Tang,

131
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:46,360
they've already pinned the blame on you.

132
00:07:46,519 --> 00:07:47,490
Why are you still acting?

133
00:07:51,439 --> 00:07:52,240
I saw everything.

134
00:07:53,060 --> 00:07:53,959
I remember it all now.

135
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:02,879
I saw you still have my childhood toys.

136
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:06,519
I remember you saved me back then.

137
00:08:20,959 --> 00:08:24,160
It was you who risked your life
to take that blade for me.

138
00:08:25,199 --> 00:08:26,240
All these years,

139
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:29,199
you've been behind me, protecting me.

140
00:08:30,350 --> 00:08:32,879
How could you have killed my parents?

141
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:35,879
Someone wanted to frame you

142
00:08:36,800 --> 00:08:38,279
and use me to do it.

143
00:08:42,480 --> 00:08:43,159
Chen,

144
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:46,360
you've really

145
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:49,399
grown up.

146
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:53,800
Let's play along.

147
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:54,780
Put on a good show.

148
00:08:54,799 --> 00:08:56,879
Tang Sihai, I'm avenging my parents today!

149
00:08:56,879 --> 00:08:58,120
Stop talking!

150
00:08:58,400 --> 00:08:58,800
No!

151
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:00,279
It has to look real

152
00:09:00,559 --> 00:09:02,120
to fool them!

153
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:03,399
Stop talking!

154
00:09:11,320 --> 00:09:12,639
You killed Madam Li, didn't you?

155
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:14,960
You were the one
who ordered Ichiro Oara.

156
00:09:15,600 --> 00:09:17,080
You brought He Lian in, right?

157
00:09:17,190 --> 00:09:18,679
Ms. Jiang works for you, doesn't she?

158
00:09:18,919 --> 00:09:21,039
And you were the one
who framed Tang Sihai!

159
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:22,960
Yes.

160
00:09:24,120 --> 00:09:25,360
I used Ms. Jiang

161
00:09:25,360 --> 00:09:26,639
to frame Tang Sihai.

162
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:28,919
But Madam Li's death
had nothing to do with me!

163
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:31,679
Quick to shift blame, aren't you?

164
00:09:32,700 --> 00:09:34,990
Don't think I won't touch you
just because you're a woman.

165
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:36,960
For what you did,

166
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:39,400
I could kill you a thousand times.

167
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:41,440
Ye Chen,

168
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:43,799
I was also under pressure,

169
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:45,279
forced into it.

170
00:09:46,399 --> 00:09:47,679
Under pressure?

171
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:49,920
Ms. Song,
that's quite the understatement.

172
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:51,799
Forget it.

173
00:09:51,880 --> 00:09:52,890
Let's not talk about this.

174
00:09:53,120 --> 00:09:53,820
You need to leave.

175
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:55,799
They're too powerful for you to fight.

176
00:09:55,919 --> 00:09:57,480
You really think I'd believe you?

177
00:09:58,039 --> 00:09:59,320
You should trust her.

178
00:10:00,612 --> 00:10:03,562
(Wu Xin, the Wu family heir)

179
00:10:14,700 --> 00:10:15,660
What are you doing here?

180
00:10:16,039 --> 00:10:17,320
Here to protect you, of course.

181
00:10:19,399 --> 00:10:20,200
Mr. Ye,

182
00:10:20,679 --> 00:10:21,399
a pleasure.

183
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:22,720
I'm Wu Xin.

184
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:25,840
Took me some time
to confirm your identity.

185
00:10:26,279 --> 00:10:26,799
I'm late.

186
00:10:27,090 --> 00:10:27,600
My apologies.

187
00:10:30,080 --> 00:10:30,679
By the way,

188
00:10:32,519 --> 00:10:33,360
I was

189
00:10:34,919 --> 00:10:36,400
controlling Ms. Song.

190
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:39,600
And I'm the one who killed

191
00:10:42,080 --> 00:10:42,787
Madam Li.

192
00:10:44,150 --> 00:10:46,100
Then you'll pay with your life!

193
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:21,488
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

194
00:12:21,575 --> 00:12:25,328
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

195
00:12:25,788 --> 00:12:30,725
♪I am fireworks, not a fire cast aside♪

196
00:12:30,888 --> 00:12:33,175
♪I open my eyes amid the ruins♪

197
00:12:33,488 --> 00:12:36,168
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

198
00:12:37,238 --> 00:12:39,863
♪Let them mock, let them sneer♪

199
00:12:40,163 --> 00:12:43,175
♪I sharpen my silence into blades♪

200
00:12:43,375 --> 00:12:46,425
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

201
00:12:46,538 --> 00:12:49,500
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

202
00:12:49,768 --> 00:12:52,925
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

203
00:12:53,150 --> 00:12:56,900
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

204
00:12:56,900 --> 00:12:59,763
♪I belong to no one♪

205
00:12:59,825 --> 00:13:03,275
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

206
00:13:03,275 --> 00:13:05,950
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

207
00:13:05,950 --> 00:13:12,288
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪
